<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>HBN-MPC Demo Videos</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #222;
      background: #ffffff;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 34px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .buttons {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .buttons a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 6px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: #2f6feb;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 45px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .video-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(420px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .video-card {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 15px;
      background: #fafafa;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    }

    .video-card video {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: #000;
    }

    .caption {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .abstract {
      text-align: justify;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    code {
      background: #f2f2f2;
      padding: 2px 5px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <h1>HBN-MPC Demo Videos</h1>

  <div class="subtitle">
    Experimental demonstration videos for energy–stability coordinated torque allocation.
  </div>

  <div class="buttons">
    <a href="https://github.com/wuweiniuniu/video">Code</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/wuweiniuniu/video/releases/latest">Videos</a>
  </div>

  <h2>Demo Videos</h2>

  <div class="video-grid">

    <div class="video-card">
      <video controls muted loop playsinline preload="metadata">
        <source src="https://github.com/wuweiniuniu/video/releases/download/v1.0.0/extreme_condition.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        Your browser does not support the video tag.
      </video>
      <div class="caption">Extreme-condition test</div>
    </div>

    <div class="video-card">
      <video controls muted loop playsinline preload="metadata">
        <source src="https://github.com/wuweiniuniu/video/releases/download/v1.0.0/mild_condition.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        Your browser does not support the video tag.
      </video>
      <div class="caption">Mild-condition test</div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <h2>Abstract</h2>

  <p class="abstract">
    This project provides MATLAB/Simulink implementation files and experimental demonstration videos
    for a hierarchical energy–stability coordinated torque allocation framework. The videos illustrate
    the controller performance under different driving conditions.
  </p>

  <h2>Repository</h2>

  <p>
    Source code and model files are available at:
    <a href="https://github.com/wuweiniuniu/video">https://github.com/wuweiniuniu/video</a>
  </p>

</body>
</html>